<h3 id='set_icon_texture'>: set_icon_texture()</h3><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight lua tab-lua"><code><span class="n">meta</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">set_icon_texture</span><span class="p">(</span> <span class="n">_modpath</span><span class="o">..</span><span class="s2">"icon.png"</span> <span class="p">)</span>
</code></pre></div>
<p><strong>For , ,  and  objects:</strong><br>
&emsp;This function assigns the <em>P.E.T. &amp; face icon</em> that will be displayed in the upper corner of the screen while you are in the overworld.</p>

<p><strong>For  objects:</strong><br>
&emsp;This function assigns the <em>chip icon</em> that will be displayed when this action is available to choose?</p>
<h4 id='function-call'>Function Call</h4>
<p><code>meta:set_icon_texture( path )</code></p>
<h4 id='parameters'>Parameters</h4>
